{"tid":1354563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咁大穫無人講? ７２１上環最恐怖１分鐘半片段流出 !!!!","createTime":"2019-07-23T07:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T13:33:05.000Z","uid":61520,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"d25d2c836aba0aea85ba3fe330976d811e1432cf","tid":1354563,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:12:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">721終極文宣片：等我用2分半鐘去話俾大家知721去唔去 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1335689\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1335689</a></span></strong><strong><br />\n首先，多謝各位巴絲係上一套文宣片支持同埋意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2bX6CKzg_5w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2bX6CKzg_5w&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQa0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=faa7b461\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2bX6CKzg_5w</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日香港人大多數focus 去晒元朗個邊，而<span style=\"color: red;\">上環同一時間搞到好大穫，義士勇武抵抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、克警發左36槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，推跌記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，義士同記者都有中槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，亦搞到中西區充斥住催淚彈既空氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>。<br />\n<br />\n今次我地團隊整左1分鐘半懶人包短片，簡述左上環暴力開槍鎮壓既經過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果琴晚唔係太清楚上環發生左咩事，比我地用分半鐘同你話俾你聽。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上環暴力開槍鎮壓   元朗恐怖分子襲擊  <br />\n#兩邊都要關注 ＃麻煩各位巴絲雙推post</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Credit比返所有樓主，幫手整合最近熱門既上環Post<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力 齊上齊落<br />\n不分化 不篤灰 不割蓆 不譴責</div></span><br />\n［整合] 7.21上環開槍清場 有片有圖！ - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1348209\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1348209</a><br />\n<br />\n黑警上環開左36槍 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1345680\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1345680</a><br />\n<br />\n721 上環開槍整合 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1348232\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1348232</a></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c33597f31c8492b42abb675a52932106d70c9365","tid":1354563,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:13:15.000Z","msg":"727 728全民大作戰終極整合POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354540</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"464c433cf15fbdb29e6146ec4297bf9d8d9b11e1","tid":1354563,"uid":39552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:13:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55ec730ec1bc5418447e384e3f0d85376872fd43","tid":1354563,"uid":162441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:52:15.000Z","msg":"推啊!!!!!!!!!推啊!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"d21900843568d9fb5a74d0a870c0ab4649d1c78d","tid":1354563,"uid":246803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:55:37.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n元朗已經有多傳媒電台facebook輿論啦<br />\n推咗兩日上環啲post都推唔到上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c0de5cf710461fb99fc43417ad62787ef56bc9","tid":1354563,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:58:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d15338993262745e20df048907c086b283210f1","tid":1354563,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:59:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11918bc4c18d07129f669544d875b744fa581855","tid":1354563,"uid":183430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:00:05.000Z","msg":"推"}